# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your python version inside the project:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if you wish to ignore Pipfile.lock:
#      Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   poetry.lock is usually committed, but in libraries it's optional
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   pdm.lock is usually committed, but in libraries it's optional
# pdm.lock

